    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns have cooked through add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli relish</strong> and the<strong> </strong>juice of your<strong> lime[s] </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 30 secs further, or until thickened</p>",
