      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> grated carrot </strong>and<strong> drained noodles & mangetout</strong> to the pan with the prawns and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>sweet chilli king prawn noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy noodle water if it's looking a little dry!</p><p>Crush your <strong>roasted peanuts </strong>with a rolling pin</p><p>Tip: If you don’t have a rolling pin, just chop them roughly!</p>",
